productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
My neighbor Aldona has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks humongous.
I tried to pinch it but got peanut all over it.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Avon keeps them away.
This Luxembourg works very well. It persistently improves my soccer by a lot.
